{"tid":1946540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用緊LG G6，換機求推薦","createTime":"2020-03-27T16:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T10:36:46.000Z","uid":148983,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8656bf57a9d3c6c50fac06d43d7ca56a327068c8","tid":1946540,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"話說小弟喺2017年嘅時候換手機，上一部用LG G3體驗良好，於是諗都冇諗就換咗G6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來發現佢用舊一代嘅U S821 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家差唔多三年，部機開始唔掂，SIM卡槽又爛咗讀唔到SD Card，好似就嚟咩都run唔到咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開始萌生換機嘅意願，自問要求有三個<br />\n1. 唔要支那牌子<br />\n2. 冇曲mon<br />\n3. 冇水滴/劉海<br />\nBonus: 防水防塵<br />\n<br />\n喺咁嚴峻嘅條件下，整理到幾部手機出嚟<br />\n1. Zenfone 6<br />\n2. Xperia 1<br />\n3. Xperia 5<br />\n4. 唔知幾時出嘅Xperia 1 II<br />\n<br />\n現時睇落Zenfone好似最抵買咁，睇啲人話Sony啲軟件好差咁又有啲卻步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底應該等埋Zenfone 7先？定直接買6？定抑或買Sony好？定買其他牌子？求意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nROG II同Zenfone 6相比太貴，冇令我買佢嘅原因，親生仔容量太小又冇得插SD Card，而且水貨冇保養，所以都不了"},{"pid":"256689f5f3bca0ac39223f5ea3d5ac51346d74dc","tid":1946540,"uid":274123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"之前都諗過入手sony,但sony得樣同相機正，個餡唔掂就冇買到，遲d iphone11再平小小個陣入手iphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917077b6ec3fe7671563040bd7367dd517c79db5","tid":1946540,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256689f5f3bca0ac39223f5ea3d5ac51346d74dc","tid":1946540,"uid":274123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"之前都諗過入手sony,但sony得樣同相機正，個餡唔掂就冇買到，遲d iphone11再平小小個陣入手iphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"之前睇Sony Xperia 1 II個發佈會好吸引，但又見到好多人話佢軟件問題一路冇改善所以都有啲卻步...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niPhone不了完全冇興趣"},{"pid":"a417fc25e904275ccf4f23fc5720d298d097960f","tid":1946540,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"Zenfone 6 都係40XX-43XX"},{"pid":"7ddf521e3da6ba0bffab0527e07cd7e2d372ef10","tid":1946540,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clublike.com.hk/asus-zenfone-6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clublike.com.hk%2Fasus-zenfone-6.html&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=544ad20a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clublike.com.hk/asus-zenfone-6.html</a>"},{"pid":"9f41d12f386fb3742ea5c00d098a81edd234b1f5","tid":1946540,"uid":84325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:58:08.000Z","msg":"Pixel 3， 減緊價兼An10，相機仲好勁"},{"pid":"ff40bcd75fb44a867abdc1e545e9723b28ab2442","tid":1946540,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f41d12f386fb3742ea5c00d098a81edd234b1f5","tid":1946540,"uid":84325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:58:08.000Z","msg":"Pixel 3， 減緊價兼An10，相機仲好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"不了，親身仔容量太細，btw邊度減價？純碎好奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a49a54edc0024586d60e3a907dbb8b13f85ac7","tid":1946540,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a417fc25e9